"""
Creation of modular symbols spaces

EXAMPLES:
    sage: C = HeckeModules(RationalField()); C
    Category of Hecke modules over Rational Field
    sage: M = ModularSymbols(11)
    sage: M.category()
    Category of Hecke modules over Rational Field
    sage: M in C
    True
"""

